sql_query.sql: SELECT "statuses"."id" FROM "statuses" WHERE "statuses"."reblog_of_id" = $1 AND "statuses"."deleted_at" IS NULL ORDER BY "statuses"."id" ASC LIMIT $2
UPDATE "statuses" SET "deleted_at" = $1 WHERE "statuses"."reblog_of_id" = $2 AND "statuses"."deleted_at" IS NULL AND "statuses"."id" = $3

SELECT "statuses"."account_id" FROM "statuses" WHERE "statuses"."deleted_at" IS NULL AND "statuses"."in_reply_to_id" = $1 ORDER BY "statuses"."id" DESC

SELECT coalesce(nullif(accounts.shared_inbox_url, ''), accounts.inbox_url) AS preferred_inbox_url FROM "accounts" WHERE "accounts"."id" IN ($1, $2) AND "accounts"."protocol" = $3 GROUP BY "preferred_inbox_url"

SELECT coalesce(nullif(accounts.shared_inbox_url, ''), accounts.inbox_url) AS preferred_inbox_url FROM "accounts" INNER JOIN "follows" ON "accounts"."id" = "follows"."account_id" WHERE "follows"."target_account_id" = $1 AND "accounts"."protocol" = $2 GROUP BY "preferred_inbox_url"
